static

Helper function for CANTX_CellTemperatures()

Used in the CANTX_CellTemperatures() callback to set invalid flag data and temperature data in the CAN frame.

Parameters
[in]muxIdmultiplexer value
[in]pMessagepointer to CAN frame data
[in]cellTemperatureSignalsignal characteristics for temperature data
[in]cellTemperatureInvalidFlagSignalsignal characteristics for invalid flag data
[in]endiannessbig or little endianness of data
[in]kpkCanShimshim to the database entries
